Company Overview of CHC Leasing (Ireland) Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CHC Leasing (Ireland) Limited offers aircraft financing and leasing services. CHC Leasing (Ireland) Limited was formerly known as Justinvale Limited and changed its name to CHC Leasing (Ireland) Limited in November 2010. The company is based in Dublin, Ireland. CHC Leasing (Ireland) Limited operates as a subsidiary of CHC Helicopter S.A.


